- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the proposed architecture relies exclusively on neural components. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is relevant as the paper discusses how program synthesis can facilitate software development. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is relevant as the paper deals with generating executable code from natural language specifications.
